<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="ru">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Anna Sherbatova — Покупки из США, Европы и Китая</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300;1,400&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --milk: #F8F5F0;
    --milk-deep: #EDE8E1;
    --black: #0E0E0E;
    --charcoal: #2C2C2C;
    --silver: #B8B8B8;
    --silver-light: #D8D5D0;
    --silver-pale: #ECECEC;
    --accent: #9A9A8A;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--milk);
    color: var(--black);
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    padding: 24px 60px;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    background: rgba(20,20,20,0.90);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    animation: fadeDown 0.8s ease both;
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: #FFFFFF;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .nav-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
  .nav-social {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    width: 36px; height: 36px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .nav-social:hover { border-color: #FFFFFF; background: #FFFFFF; color: var(--black); }
  .nav-cta {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: #FFFFFF;
    text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 24px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: #FFFFFF; color: var(--black); }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  #hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    padding-top: 80px;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-left {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
    padding: 80px 60px 80px 60px;
    background: #1A1A1A;
    animation: fadeUp 1s 0.2s ease both;
  }
  .hero-tag {
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  }
  .hero-tag::before {
    content: ''; display: block;
    width: 32px; height: 1px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(48px, 5vw, 76px);
    font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1;
    color: #FFFFFF; margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .hero-title em { font-style: italic; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); }
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.9;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72); max-width: 420px; margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
  .hero-cta-group { display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #FFFFFF; color: #0E0E0E;
    padding: 16px 36px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--milk-deep); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-ghost {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    padding-bottom: 2px; transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover { color: #FFFFFF; border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }

  .hero-right {
    position: relative; background: var(--milk-deep);
    display: flex; align-items: flex-end; justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    animation: fadeIn 1.2s 0.4s ease both;
  }
  .hero-visual-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 60% 40%, rgba(184,184,184,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }
  .hero-monogram {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 320px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1;
    color: rgba(14,14,14,0.04); letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    position: absolute; bottom: -40px; right: -20px;
    pointer-events: none; user-select: none;
  }
  .hero-card {
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    margin: 60px 40px;
    background: var(--milk); padding: 40px;
    border: 1px solid var(--silver-pale);
    max-width: 360px; width: 100%;
    animation: fadeUp 1s 0.6s ease both;
  }
  .hero-card-label {
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--silver); margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .hero-stats {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .stat-item {}
  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 42px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1;
    color: var(--black); margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .hero-directions {
    display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .dir-tag {
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--charcoal); padding: 6px 12px;
    background: var(--milk-deep); border: 1px solid var(--silver-pale);
  }

  /* ── SECTION BASE ── */
  section { padding: 120px 60px; }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.35em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--silver); margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  }
  .section-label::after {
    content: ''; flex: 1; max-width: 40px;
    height: 1px; background: var(--silver-light);
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 56px); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--black); margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .section-title em { font-style: italic; }
  .section-body {
    font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.9; color: var(--charcoal);
  }

  /* ── ABOUT ── */
  #about {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
    background: #1C1C1C; color: var(--milk);
    padding: 120px 60px;
  }
  #about .section-label { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
  #about .section-label::after { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
  #about .section-title { color: #FFFFFF; }
  #about .section-body { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82); }
  .about-photo-area {
    position: relative; aspect-ratio: 3/4; max-height: 540px;
    background: #2A2A2A;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .about-photo-placeholder {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 120px; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
  }
  .about-photo-label {
    position: absolute; bottom: 24px; left: 24px;
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  }
  .about-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); margin-top: 40px;
  }
  .about-fact {
    background: #222222; padding: 24px;
    font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72); line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .about-fact strong {
    display: block; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 28px; font-weight: 300; color: #FFFFFF;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  /* ── TELEGRAM ── */
  #telegram { background: var(--milk); }
  .tg-inner {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .tg-features { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; margin-top: 48px; }
  .tg-feature {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr; gap: 20px;
    padding: 28px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--silver-pale);
    align-items: start;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
  }
  .tg-feature:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--silver-pale); }
  .tg-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 22px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--silver);
    padding-top: 2px;
  }
  .tg-text h4 {
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--black); margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .tg-text p {
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--accent); line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .tg-visual {
    background: var(--charcoal); padding: 48px 40px;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .tg-visual-icon {
    font-size: 64px; margin-bottom: 24px; display: block;
    filter: grayscale(1) brightness(2);
  }
  .tg-visual h3 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 32px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--milk);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .tg-visual p {
    font-size: 12px; color: rgba(248,245,240,0.5); line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .tg-visual .btn-milk {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--milk); color: var(--black);
    padding: 14px 28px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .tg-visual .btn-milk:hover { background: var(--silver-pale); }
  .tg-bg-text {
    position: absolute; bottom: -20px; right: -10px;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 180px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* ── GUIDE ── */
  #guide {
    background: var(--milk-deep);
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .guide-mockup {
    position: relative; aspect-ratio: 3/4; max-height: 500px;
  }
  .guide-card-back {
    position: absolute; top: 20px; left: 20px; right: -20px; bottom: -20px;
    background: var(--silver-pale); border: 1px solid var(--silver-light);
  }
  .guide-card-front {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: var(--black);
    padding: 48px 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  }
  .guide-card-top {
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); margin-bottom: auto;
  }
  .guide-card-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 36px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--milk);
    line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .guide-card-list {
    list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;
  }
  .guide-card-list li {
    font-size: 11px; color: rgba(248,245,240,0.5); letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  }
  .guide-card-list li::before {
    content: '—'; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); font-size: 10px;
  }
  .guide-right .section-body { margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .guide-included {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0;
    margin: 32px 0 40px;
  }
  .guide-item {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--silver-pale);
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--charcoal);
  }
  .guide-item:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--silver-pale); }
  .guide-item span { color: var(--silver); font-size: 11px; }
  .guide-free-label {
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  /* ── REVIEWS ── */
  #reviews { background: var(--milk); }
  .reviews-header {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }
  .reviews-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1px;
    background: var(--silver-pale);
  }
  .review-card {
    background: var(--milk); padding: 40px 36px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  .review-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }
  .review-stars {
    display: flex; gap: 3px; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .star {
    width: 14px; height: 14px;
    background: var(--black); clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 61% 35%, 98% 35%, 68% 57%, 79% 91%, 50% 70%, 21% 91%, 32% 57%, 2% 35%, 39% 35%);
  }
  .review-text {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 18px; font-weight: 300; font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.6; color: var(--charcoal); margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .review-author {
    font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--silver);
  }
  .review-author strong {
    display: block; color: var(--black); font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 2px; font-style: normal;
  }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  #cta {
    background: var(--black); text-align: center;
    padding: 140px 60px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cta-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 60%, rgba(184,184,184,0.06) 0%, transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .cta-bg-text {
    position: absolute; bottom: -60px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 280px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.025); white-space: nowrap;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  #cta .section-label {
    justify-content: center; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  }
  #cta .section-label::after { display: none; }
  #cta .section-title { color: var(--milk); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  #cta .section-body { color: rgba(248,245,240,0.5); max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto 48px; }
  .cta-form {
    display: flex; gap: 0; max-width: 460px; margin: 0 auto 24px;
  }
  .cta-input {
    flex: 1; padding: 16px 20px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    border-right: none; color: var(--milk);
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    outline: none; transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .cta-input::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); }
  .cta-input:focus { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }
  .cta-btn {
    padding: 16px 28px; background: var(--milk); color: var(--black);
    border: none; cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: all 0.3s; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .cta-btn:hover { background: var(--silver-pale); }
  .cta-or {
    font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    margin: 0 0 20px;
  }
  .btn-tg {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color: var(--milk);
    padding: 16px 36px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .btn-tg:hover { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); }
  .cta-note {
    font-size: 10px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-top: 28px;
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    background: var(--black); padding: 32px 60px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  }
  .footer-socials { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .footer-copy {
    font-size: 10px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
  .footer-link {
    font-size: 10px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-decoration: none; text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }
  .footer-link:hover { color: var(--milk); }

  /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes fadeDown {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-12px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }

  .reveal {
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    nav { padding: 20px 24px; }
    section { padding: 80px 24px; }
    #hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; min-height: auto; }
    .hero-left { padding: 100px 24px 60px; }
    .hero-right { display: none; }
    #about { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 80px 24px; gap: 48px; }
    .about-photo-area { max-height: 320px; }
    .tg-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    #guide { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .guide-mockup { display: none; }
    .reviews-header { flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start; }
    .reviews-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    #cta { padding: 100px 24px; }
    .cta-form { flex-direction: column; }
    .cta-input { border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-bottom: none; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; padding: 24px; text-align: center; }
  }
</style>

</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->

<nav>
  <a href="#hero" class="nav-logo">Anna Sherbatova</a>
  <div class="nav-right">
    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/annasherbatova?igsh=OTIxcTJnYW1pdnBm&utm_source=qr" target="_blank" class="nav-social" title="Instagram">
      <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="0.8" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg>
    </a>
    <a href="https://t.me/zakupki_china_GA" target="_blank" class="nav-cta">Telegram</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->

<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-left">
    <div class="hero-tag">Эксперт по зарубежным покупкам</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      Лучшее из США,<br>
      Европы<br>
      <em>и Китая —</em><br>
      к вашей двери
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">
      Знаю, как купить оригинал без переплат, обойти ограничения и доставить всё — безопасно, быстро, легально. Делюсь только проверенным.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-cta-group">
      <a href="https://t.me/zakupki_china_GA" target="_blank" class="btn-primary">Подписаться на канал</a>
      <a href="#guide" class="btn-ghost">Получить гайд</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-right">
    <div class="hero-visual-bg"></div>
    <div class="hero-monogram">AS</div>
    <div class="hero-card reveal">
      <div class="hero-card-label">Expertise</div>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-num">3</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Направления</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-num">5+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Лет практики</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-num">15+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Посредников</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-num">∞</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Брендов</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-directions">
        <div class="dir-tag">США</div>
        <div class="dir-tag">Европа</div>
        <div class="dir-tag">Китай</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->

<section id="about">
  <div class="about-photo-area reveal">
